JsScratch is a Sratch program viewer for Javscript and HTML

JsScratch runs using the HTML5 canvas element JavaScript

To use the player follow these steps:

1. Place your .sb file (Sratch File) in the same folder as player.html

2. Open player.html in a editor

3. Change the string 'Pacman.sb' to your .sb name

4. Open the Program in a browser and enjoy!

For more information and demos please see http://jsscratch.co.cc/

Scratch Programming Language: http://scratch.mit.edu/

